{"tid":2104773,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"【BNO】胡錫進抨西方虛偽：為何只放寬港人移民 14億內地人無份？","createTime":"2020-07-12T07:58:52.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-12T08:13:10.000Z","uid":105567,"like":3,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"17fca6fa037dc9a3a410fdc1a2726226f84ebd3f","tid":2104773,"uid":105567,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-12T07:58:52.000Z","msg":"港區國安法訂立後，英國及澳洲等國家公布放寬香港人移民計劃，令中國與西方角力火上澆油，中國官方多次抨擊外國干涉內政。環球時報總編輯胡錫進在微博再發文評論此事，質疑西方以「人權」為由修改移民政策，為何只讓香港人移民當地，卻沒讓內地14億人同享。他直指西方國家虛偽。<br />\n<br />\n胡錫進周六在微博發帖，再度談論英澳等西方國家計劃放鬆政策，吸納香港人移民當地。他直指，「最近，不僅英國，其他西方國家也有一些表示要因爲國安法『庇護香港人』，給他們提供簽證和居留權等。作秀呵」。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://china.hket.com/article/2693252/%E3%80%90BNO%E3%80%91%E8%83%A1%E9%8C%AB%E9%80%B2%E6%8A%A8%E8%A5%BF%E6%96%B9%E8%99%9B%E5%81%BD%EF%BC%9A%E7%82%BA%E4%BD%95%E5%8F%AA%E6%94%BE%E5%AF%AC%E6%B8%AF%E4%BA%BA%E7%A7%BB%E6%B0%91%20%2014%E5%84%84%E5%85%A7%E5%9C%B0%E4%BA%BA%E7%84%A1%E4%BB%BD%EF%BC%9F\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fchina.hket.com%2Farticle%2F2693252%2F%25E3%2580%2590BNO%25E3%2580%2591%25E8%2583%25A1%25E9%258C%25AB%25E9%2580%25B2%25E6%258A%25A8%25E8%25A5%25BF%25E6%2596%25B9%25E8%2599%259B%25E5%2581%25BD%25EF%25BC%259A%25E7%2582%25BA%25E4%25BD%2595%25E5%258F%25AA%25E6%2594%25BE%25E5%25AF%25AC%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E7%25A7%25BB%25E6%25B0%2591%2520%252014%25E5%2584%2584%25E5%2585%25A7%25E5%259C%25B0%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E7%2584%25A1%25E4%25BB%25BD%25EF%25BC%259F&d=GdzNT1%2FdEV%2FiwqmWSoLNnsRCHeky4xD%2FQbA%2BfbsvJuc%3D&h=8c9296ee\" target=\"_blank\">https://china.hket.com/article/2693252/%E3%80%90BNO%E3%80%91%E8%83%A1%E9%8C%AB%E9%80%B2%E6%8A%A8%E8%A5%BF%E6%96%B9%E8%99%9B%E5%81%BD%EF%BC%9A%E7%82%BA%E4%BD%95%E5%8F%AA%E6%94%BE%E5%AF%AC%E6%B8%AF%E4%BA%BA%E7%A7%BB%E6%B0%91%20%2014%E5%84%84%E5%85%A7%E5%9C%B0%E4%BA%BA%E7%84%A1%E4%BB%BD%EF%BC%9F</a>"},{"pid":"381631d24071577b145da27d2b1b6b57d934ba8d","tid":2104773,"uid":105567,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-12T08